### 🧪 Database Design & Constraints HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# 1. Ambil List User Beserta Relasi Pesanan
GET {{host}}/api/design/users

###

# 2. Buat User Valid (Lolos Seluruh Constraint)
POST {{host}}/api/design/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "eko_patrio",
  "email": "eko@gmail.com",
  "age": 35
}

###

# 3. Buat User dengan Email Duplikat (Melanggar UNIQUE Constraint)
# Skenario: Error DB dibalikkan dengan penjelasan penolakan UNIQUE index
POST {{host}}/api/design/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "eko_baru",
  "email": "habibie@gmail.com",
  "age": 25
}

###

# 4. Buat User dengan Umur Tidak Valid (Melanggar CHECK Constraint CK_Users_Age)
# Skenario: DB membatalkan simpan data karena Age diluar rentang 0-150
POST {{host}}/api/design/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bayi_ajaib",
  "email": "bayi@gmail.com",
  "age": 200
}
